#. <section class="sutta" id="an9.83"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an9.83:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 9"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 9"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an9.83:0.2"
msgid "9. Iddhipādavagga"
msgstr "9. Bases of Psychic Power"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 83. Sikkhasutta → sikkhādubbalyaiddhipādasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an9.83:0.3"
msgid "83. Sikkhasutta"
msgstr "83. Weaknesses in Training and the Bases of Psychic Power"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an9.83:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcimāni, bhikkhave, sikkhādubbalyāni."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these five weaknesses when you’re training."

msgctxt "an9.83:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an9.83:1.3"
msgid "Pāṇātipāto … pe … surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"Killing living creatures, stealing, sexual misconduct, lying, and using "
"alcoholic drinks that cause negligence."

msgctxt "an9.83:1.4"
msgid "imāni kho, bhikkhave, pañca sikkhādubbalyāni."
msgstr "These are the five weaknesses when you’re training."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.464"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an9.83:2.1"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pañcannaṃ sikkhādubbalyānaṃ pahānāya cattāro "
"iddhipādā bhāvetabbā."
msgstr ""
"To give up these five weaknesses in your training you should develop the "
"four bases of psychic power."

msgctxt "an9.83:2.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an9.83:2.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu chandasamādhipadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ "
"bhāveti, "
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops the basis of psychic power that has immersion "
"due to enthusiasm, and active effort. "

msgctxt "an9.83:2.4"
msgid "vīriyasamādhi …"
msgstr ""
"They develop the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to energy, "
"and active effort."

msgctxt "an9.83:2.5"
msgid "cittasamādhi …"
msgstr ""
"They develop the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to mental "
"development, and active effort."

msgctxt "an9.83:2.6"
msgid "vīmaṃsāsamādhipadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti."
msgstr ""
"They develop the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to inquiry, "
"and active effort."

msgctxt "an9.83:2.7"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pañcannaṃ sikkhādubbalyānaṃ pahānāya ime cattāro "
"iddhipādā bhāvetabbā”ti."
msgstr ""
"To give up those five weaknesses in your training you should develop these "
"four bases of psychic power.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.83:2.8"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
